body_html: You are not saving tf.InteractiveSession() into any variable, so it gets garbage collected. Jupyter has helper variable _ which stores output of last expression, so in first case this variable prevents your session from getting gc'ed. In the second case, the output of your cell is result of print, so your session doesn't get stored anywhere

body: You are not saving `tf.InteractiveSession()` into any variable, so it gets garbage collected. Jupyter has helper variable `_` which stores output of last expression, so in first case this variable prevents your session from getting gc'ed. In the second case, the output of your cell is result of `print`, so your session doesn't get stored anywhere
